{"id":49,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":49,"title":"Chapter 46: Jesus Christ Teaches and Prays with the Nephites","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 46","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 46"],["h1","Jesus Christ Teaches and Prays with the Nephites"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p3"},"The Nephites who saw Jesus Christ told their friends he would be back the next day. Many people worked very hard to get to where Jesus would be."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.2-3"},"3 Nephi 19:2–3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p5"},"The next morning Nephi and the other disciples taught the group that had gathered. The disciples then prayed that they would receive the Holy Ghost."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.6-9"},"3 Nephi 19:6–9"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p7"},"Nephi went into the water and was baptized. Then he baptized the other disciples."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.11-12"},"3 Nephi 19:11–12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p9"},"After they were baptized, the disciples received the Holy Ghost. Fire seemed to surround them, and angels came down from heaven and ministered unto them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.13-14"},"3 Nephi 19:13–14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p11"},"While the angels were with the disciples, Jesus came and stood among them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.15"},"3 Nephi 19:15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p13"},"Christ told all the Nephites to kneel on the ground. He told his disciples to pray."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.16-17"},"3 Nephi 19:16–17"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p15"},"While they were praying, Jesus went a little way off from the people and knelt down and prayed to Heavenly Father."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.18-20"},"3 Nephi 19:18–20"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p17"},"Jesus thanked Heavenly Father for giving the Holy Ghost to his disciples. Then he asked for the Holy Ghost to be given to anyone who believed the disciples’ words."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.20-21"},"3 Nephi 19:20–21"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p19"},"Jesus blessed his disciples while they were praying. He smiled at them, and they became as white as his face and clothing."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.25"},"3 Nephi 19:25"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p21"},"Jesus prayed again for his disciples. He was pleased with their great faith."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.29,35"},"3 Nephi 19:29, 35"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p23"},"Christ told the people to stop praying but to keep praying in their hearts. Then he gave them the sacrament."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.1-5"},"3 Nephi 20:1–5"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f12"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_12.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p25","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p25"},"No one had brought bread or wine, but the Savior provided it in a miraculous way."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p26"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.6-7"},"3 Nephi 20:6–7"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f13"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_13.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p27","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p27"},"Jesus Christ told the Nephites that his gospel would be brought back to the earth in the last days."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p28"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.1,3,7,9"},"3 Nephi 21:1, 3, 7, 9"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f14"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_14.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p29"},"He told them to study the scriptures, and he had Nephi write in the records the fulfillment of the rest of Samuel the Lamanite’s prophecies."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p30","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p30"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/23.1,9-13"},"3 Nephi 23:1, 9–13"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f15"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_15.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p31","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p31"},"Then Jesus taught the people from the scriptures. He told them to teach one another the things he had taught them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p32","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p32"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/23.14"},"3 Nephi 23:14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f16"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_16.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p33","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p33"},"Jesus went back up to heaven, and his disciples taught the people. Those who believed were baptized and received the Holy Ghost."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p34","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p34"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/26.15,17"},"3 Nephi 26:15, 17"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.f17"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_049_17.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p35","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p35"},"The Nephites began to obey all the commandments."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-46-jesus-christ-teaches-and-prays-with-the-nephites.p36"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/26.20"},"3 Nephi 26:20"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
